    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと&lt;DIO&gt;、
バタバタしないの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey &lt;DIO&gt;, stop flailing around!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>妹が、兄貴に命令すんなよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A little sister shouldn’t boss her big brother around!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何言ってんの？
私がお姉ちゃん、&lt;DIO&gt;は弟でしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What are you talking about? I’m the big sister, and &lt;DIO&gt; is the little brother!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39648</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレの方が上だ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I’m the older one!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40060</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう……エトぉ！
お姉ちゃんはわたしだよね？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh… Ethos! I’m the big sister, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だから、わかんないってば</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I told you, I don’t know!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふたり一緒にぼくんとこに来たんだって。
前から何度も言ってるでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You both came to me together. I’ve told you this many times before.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42096</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ、もう……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez, come on…</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よーし！　今日こそ虫とり対決で、
白黒はっきりつけるぞ、&lt;MEL&gt;！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright! Today, we’ll settle this with a bug-catching contest, &lt;MEL&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43600</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_001_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もうっ！　お子ちゃまっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh! You’re such a child!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
